# U-ITE â€” Internet Truth Engine

U-ITE is a cross-platform diagnostic tool that tells the **truth** about where internet problems really exist:
- Local device
- Router / LAN
- ISP
- DNS
- Application layer

It performs layered network checks and stores historical results for future analysis.

## Features
- Auto-detects router (default gateway)
- Layered connectivity diagnostics
- Latency & packet loss analysis
- Cross-platform (Linux, macOS, Windows)
- Persistent local storage (SQLite)

